      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1764491925648,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Practice Question.1: find the area of a square.\n\nFlowchart:                        Pseudo-code\n                                  1. input a\n                                  2. area = a * a\n                                  3. print area\n                                  4. exit                \n            \n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------\n\nPractice Question.2: find the minimum of two numbers.\n\nFlowchart:                        Pseudo-code\n                                  1. input a & b\n                                  2. if a > b\n                                        print b\n                                  3. else\n                                        print a\n                                  4. Exit\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------\n\nPractice Question.3: find is a number even or odd.\n\nPractice Question.4: find the sum of numbers from 1 to N.\n\nFlowchart:                                                       Pseudocode:\n                                                                 1. input N\n                                                                 2. count=1, sum=0\n                                                                 3. while count <= N\n                                                                    sum = sum+count\n                                                                    count = count+1\n                                                                 4. print sum\n                                                                 5. Exit\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------\n\nPractice Question.5: find a given number is prime or not\n\nFlowchart:                                                       Pseudocode:\n                                                                 1. input N\n                                                                 2. i=2\n                                                                 3. while i <= (N-1)\n                                                                    if N%i==0\n                                                                      print non-prime\n                                                                      Exit\n                                                                    else\n                                                                      i=i+1\n                                                                 4. print prime\n                                                                 5. Exit",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 8,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Practice Question.1: find the area of a square.\n\nFlowchart:                        Pseudo-code\n                                  1. input a\n                                  2. area = a * a\n                                  3. print area\n                                  4. exit                \n            \n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------\n\nPractice Question.2: find the minimum of two numbers.\n\nFlowchart:                        Pseudo-code\n                                  1. input a & b\n                                  2. if a > b\n                                        print b\n                                  3. else\n                                        print a\n                                  4. Exit\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------\n\nPractice Question.3: find is a number even or odd.\n\nPractice Question.4: find the sum of numbers from 1 to N.\n\nFlowchart:                                                       Pseudocode:\n                                                                 1. input N\n                                                                 2. count=1, sum=0\n                                                                 3. while count <= N\n                                                                    sum = sum+count\n                                                                    count = count+1\n                                                                 4. print sum\n                                                                 5. Exit\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------\n\nPractice Question.5: find a given number is prime or not\n\nFlowchart:                                                       Pseudocode:\n                                                                 1. input N\n                                                                 2. i=2\n                                                                 3. while i <= (N-1)\n                                                                    if N%i==0\n                                                                      print non-prime\n                                                                      Exit\n                                                                    else\n                                                                      i=i+1\n                                                                 4. print prime\n                                                                 5. Exit",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
